msgstr "获取项目中可用蜘蛛的名称。"

#: ../../../topics/api.rst:210
msgid ""
"List the spiders' names that can handle the given request. Will try to match "
"the request's url against the domains of the spiders."
msgstr "列出可以处理给定请求的蜘蛛名称。将尝试匹配请求的URL与蜘蛛的域名。"

#: ../../../topics/api.rst:213
