#: ../../../topics/api.rst:231
msgid "Stats Collector API"
msgstr "统计数据收集器 API"

#: ../../../topics/api.rst:233
msgid ""
"There are several Stats Collectors available under the :mod:`scrapy."
"statscollectors` module and they all implement the Stats Collector API "
"defined by the :class:`~scrapy.statscollectors.StatsCollector` class (which "
"they all inherit from)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/api.rst:245
msgid ""
"Return the value for the given stats key or default if it doesn't exist."
msgstr "返回给定状态键值或默认值，如果它不存在。"

#: ../../../topics/api.rst:249
msgid "Get all stats from the currently running spider as a dict."
msgstr "从当前运行的蜘蛛获取所有的统计信息作为一种词典。"

#: ../../../topics/api.rst:253
msgid "Set the given value for the given stats key."
msgstr "设置给定统计键的给定值。"

#: ../../../topics/api.rst:257
msgid "Override the current stats with the dict passed in ``stats`` argument."
msgstr "使用 ``stats`` 参数覆盖当前的统计信息。"

#: ../../../topics/api.rst:261
msgid ""
"Increment the value of the given stats key, by the given count, assuming the "
"start value given (when it's not set)."
msgstr ""
"通过给定的计数增加给定统计数据的值，假定给定的起始值 (当它没有设置时)。"

#: ../../../topics/api.rst:266
msgid ""
"Set the given value for the given key only if current value for the same key "
"is lower than value. If there is no current value for the given key, the "
"value is always set."
msgstr ""
"仅在同一键的当前值小于值时设置给定的键值。 如果给定的键值没有当前值，则该值总"
"是被设置的。"

#: ../../../topics/api.rst:272
msgid ""
"Set the given value for the given key only if current value for the same key "
"is greater than value. If there is no current value for the given key, the "
"value is always set."
msgstr ""
"只有当同一键的当前值大于值时，才设置给定的键值。 如果给定的键值没有当前值，则"
"该值总是被设置的。"

#: ../../../topics/api.rst:278
msgid "Clear all stats."
msgstr "清除所有数据"

#: ../../../topics/api.rst:280
msgid ""
"The following methods are not part of the stats collection api but instead "
"used when implementing custom stats collectors:"
msgstr ""
"以下方法不是统计数据收集api的一部分，而是在实现自定义统计数据收集器时使用："

#: ../../../topics/api.rst:285
msgid "Open the spider for stats collection."
msgstr "打开拼写器来收集数据。"

#: ../../../topics/api.rst:289
msgid ""
"Close the spider. After this is called, no more specific stats can be "
"accessed or collected."
msgstr "关闭拼写器。调用后无法访问或收集更多特定的统计数据。"

#: ../../../topics/api.rst:293
msgid "Engine API"
msgstr "引擎 API"

#: ../../../../scrapy/core/engine.py:docstring of
#: scrapy.core.engine.ExecutionEngine.needs_backout:1
msgid ""
"Returns ``True`` if no more requests can be sent at the moment, or ``False`` "
"otherwise."
msgstr "返回``True`` ，如果目前没有更多的请求可以发送，或者返回``False`` 。"
